    "body": "This is might different in many ways and many people,\r\nbut sometime the Api+apps never get ping request. even more than 20 minute.\r\nso we dont give pong reply back.\r\n\r\nwe also use pollMessage() on loop forever, \r\n\r\nso its like connection getDisconnected without even we knowing it, when the time coming we want to make tx, fwrite got error warning.\r\n\r\nany idea to prevent this ?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2013-07-14T13:39:14Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "body": "answer : no prevent I think, we must use own counter to measure the timeout time, use onGetServerProperties event to get exact time. if exceed the time/timeout, then force to disconnect() and reconnect and relogin again. \r\nThanks for follow up",
